These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, fanta
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | sprite | lemonade | fanta   |
| Sport      | snowboarding    | rowing  | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, russian, indian
1. the colombian is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the russian is on the far left##1
3. the russian is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | almond-milk     | milk      |
| Nationality   | russian | colombian | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, cola
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, pear, orange
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person eating pear##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating orange##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | cola  | hot-chocolate       |
| Food       | blueberry     | pear | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, artichoke, eggplant
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading, rock-climbing
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | eggplant    | artichoke     | kiwi |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | reading     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, goldfish
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, ship
1. the person driving the bike is the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | hamster | ferret     | goldfish |
| Transport   | ship        | helicopter | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, zucchini, pomegranate
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, subway, bike
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | pomegranate | cauliflower      | zucchini  |
| Transport   | scooter       | subway | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, electronic, house
3 different pets are kept: bird, horse, rabbit
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of electronic is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | house      | punk     | electronic    |
| Pet           | bird | rabbit | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
