2. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person eating banana is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | cucumber | apricot | banana      |
| Hobby   | gardening     | dancing | reading |

