.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, coffee
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | juice    | coffee    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | satire | time-travel |

