The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, mechanic
1. the doctor is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating tomato is in the middle##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | grapes     | tomato   | peas     |
| Job    | mechanic | doctor | bartender |

