1. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
2. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | cola  | almond-milk | water  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | country   | r&b |

