The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | carrot | plum   | banana        |
| Sport   | surfing    | cycling | basketball |

