.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, board-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, blues, jazz
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of jazz##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | video-games | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | metal | jazz     | blues  |

