.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, asparagus, plum
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, golf
1. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person eating orange##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | plum | orange       | asparagus  |
| Sport   | golf  | skiing | lacrosse |

 